Created files:
- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Tests/Runtime/TestSupport/TestMainThreadPump.cs
    Shared helper that drives Flush callbacks without relying on PlayerLoop.
    Holds a list of Action callbacks registered through Register(Action) which
    returns an IDisposable that removes the entry on Dispose. Pump() invokes
    every registered callback once; Pump(int frames) invokes them frames
    times. Negative frame counts and null callbacks throw.
- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Tests/Runtime/TestSupport/FakeClock.cs
    Deterministic FakeClock for time-dependent tests. Default start is
    2026-01-01T00:00:00+00:00; UtcNow returns the current virtual time.
    ScheduleAfter(delay, callback) registers an Action that fires when
    Advance(delta) reaches its due time, callbacks fire in due-time order,
    and the returned IDisposable cancels a pending callback. Negative delay,
    negative delta, and null callbacks throw.
- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Tests/Runtime/TestSupport/TestMainThreadPumpTests.cs
    6 NUnit tests for TestMainThreadPump (Pump invokes all registered
    callbacks, Pump(N) invokes per-frame, Dispose removes the registration,
    Dispose is idempotent, null callback rejected, negative frames rejected).
- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Tests/Runtime/TestSupport/FakeClockTests.cs
    8 NUnit tests for FakeClock (default start, Advance moves UtcNow forward,
    callbacks fire at-or-before target, due-order, Dispose cancels, negative
    advance/delay rejected, null callback rejected).
- Packages/com.vtuber-system-base.core-ipc-foundation/Tests/Runtime/RuntimeAssemblySmokeTests.cs
